<br>
1)What is a good BP for a 32 warrior? I've got a Validus Custodus BP, but I noticed the stats are kinda low when compared to the chest armor of some of my compatriot mercs.<br>
<br>
2)1hs? I have two (for duel wielding), a Blackened alloy longsword and a giant militia longsword, but I noticed the latter kinda sucks. I will stick with the BALS, if only because it lets me see in the dark (human+dark cave=something very bad), plus its really not that bad. But, any ideas for replacing the other?<br>
<br>
3)Places to hunt. I know there are a lot, from GD to Kaesora to whatever, but what are the best? Where could I take a good group (Being LfB, that is easy) and get good exp and/or loot? I know there has to be some good places out there, where some of ya'll level'd up fast, but where are they?<br>
<br>
Just the three for now, and I know their long, but any help would really be appreciated. Thanks!<br>
<br>
Oh, and, ya ha har har har! Lust fer Blood! <p><br>
<br>
<br>
