<br>
2. More 1HS than it's possible to list.  I like centi weapons, but again, just check the bazaar.  If you're rich, buy priceless.<br>
<br>
3. Paw &amp; KK for xp.  For loot, hit CC, sol a/b, permafrost, MM, or even the outside of CT.  It will mostly be FS/plat -- you'll have to target your rares specifically to get something you might want or can resell. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=sarhea>Sarhea</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>walking the fine line since October 2001</span><br>  Posts: 2595<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/13/03 1:25:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=199.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://sarshouse.homestead.com/files/images/Sarhea_Nah_Nah.gif height=99, width=42></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Questions from a 32 warrior</span><hr size=1> As far as armor, I'd say the acrylia plate is getting very affordable...also, if you're not agnostic, look into the lower version of cultural armor..you're human, so look for Imbued field plate.<br>
<br>
I wore mine for a good long time.<br>
<br>
Weapons, look for lower delay type weapons. Centi shortsword is mostly unbeatable, imho for your level range, and it's worth working your 1hb skill up for a goranga spiked club.<br>
<br>
